data.title: Gabrielle Stanton
data.meta_description: Gabrielle Gail Stanton is an American television writer and producer. She is known for her work on the ABC series Grey's Anatomy and Ugly Betty, for The CW's The Flash, and for Syfy's Stephen King adaptation series Haven.
